                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>Every one of the 4 corners has got 3 columns, it is very big and hollow, is made of stone and has a bust on a pedestal in the middle, it is very heavily decorated and carved all over. Roof/top of building borne up by three columns in each corner. On top of ceiling inside is a diamond shape with quatrefoil `underneath'. On all sides outside) is a chi rho. Inside house is a bust on a pedestal. Pedestal has columns in all corners. Bust is a figure of the deceased, probably.</summary>
